   \strong{W} Weaknesses \tab Current vulnerabilities \tab \code{sensitivity_score} (VI), heat/cold AF\% (af), stratum RR inequality (sensitivity) \cr
   \strong{O} Opportunities \tab Intervention windows \tab Low VI percentile (VI), low current exposure (VI) \cr
   \strong{T} Threats \tab Climate-health risks \tab \code{exposure_score} + \code{vi_score} (VI), heat RR at P95 (dlnm), attributable number (burden), max stratum RR (sensitivity) \cr
